.TH "TODOPRO DATA PURGE" "1" "2026-02-27" "1.0.0" "todopro data purge Manual"
.SH NAME
todopro\-data\-purge \- Delete ALL your data (tasks, projects,...
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B todopro data purge
[OPTIONS]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Delete ALL your data (tasks, projects, labels, contexts, encryption keys).
.PP
⚠️  WARNING: This action CANNOT be undone!
.PP
You should export your data first:
    todopro data export --output backup.json
.PP
Examples:
    todopro data purge --dry-run  # Preview only
    todopro data purge             # Actually delete
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-dry\-run\fP
Preview what would be deleted without actually deleting
